{"title":"Zwift Games Start in March – Here’s How to Compete","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2024-zwift-games/","date":1708974035000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-banner.jpg\" alt=\"2024 zwift games promo image\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-banner.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-banner-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-banner-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-banner-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-banner-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-banner-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-banner-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></p>\n<p>While MyWhoosh has taken the World Tour races, the original online cycling world has launched competitions for the rest of us with the inaugural Zwift Games.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Running throughout March 2024, the Zwift Games feature community racing for all abilities with a five-stage series. Registration is open now, and the series runs from March 1-17. Make-up events for each stage will follow from March 18-31, and all events are category-enforced with a mix of sprint, endurance, and climbing stages and schedules to suit every racer.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Complete all five stages and you’ll find yourself in the General Classification challenge, competing for the best overall time across all five stages. Race each stage as many times as you want to log your best overall total, and track your rank on <a href=\"https://zwiftpower.com/league.php?id=2148\">Zwift Power</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What routes are in the Zwift Games?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-1.jpg\"><img width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-1.jpg\" alt=\"2024 zwift games stage 1 course map\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-1.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-1-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-1-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-1-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-1-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It depends on your category, but there are four new courses created just for the Games, albeit cobbled together from their existing maps. Stage 1 is the Loop de Loop, and it’s a sprint.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-2.jpg\"><img width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-2.jpg\" alt=\"2024 zwift games stage 2 course map\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-2.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-2-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-2-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-2-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-2-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Stage 2 is the Jurassic Coast, a short, mostly flat TT (ignore that elevation profile, total elevation is just 212m).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3ab.jpg\"><img width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3ab.jpg\" alt=\"2024 zwift games stage 3 a-b course map\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3ab.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3ab-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3ab-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3ab-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3ab-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3ab-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3ab-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For Category A/B racers, Stage 3 (the “Epic Stage”) is a monster 81.5km lap with looped out-and-back extension.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3cd.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3cd.jpg\" alt=\"2024 zwift games stage 3 c-d course map\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3cd.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3cd-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3cd-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3cd-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3cd-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3cd-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-3cd-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For Category C/D racers, Stage 3 loops through Titans Grove before circling up and down the volcano, offering two KOM sections to fool you into gassing yourself mid-stage.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-4.jpg\" alt=\"2024 zwift games stage 4 course map\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-4.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-4-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-4-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-4-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-4-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-4-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Stage 4 is shared by all categories and runs through Glasgow in a circuit for five laps.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5am.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5am.jpg\" alt=\"2024 zwift games stage 5 a-b course map\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5am.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5am-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5am-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5am-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5am-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5am-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5am-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Stage 5 for A/B category racers is a relentless, steep, 17.3km uphill climbing challenge with plenty of corners to try to take your mind off the pain.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5cd.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5cd.jpg\" alt=\"2024 zwift games stage 5 c-d course map\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5cd.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5cd-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5cd-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5cd-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5cd-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5cd-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-route-map-stage-5cd-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Stage 5 for C/D category riders is a hill climb with mountain top finish. It’s an all-out effort, but mercifully shorter than the A/B race, so you could give it a few goes on different days.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Do the Zwift Games have prizes?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-adidas-cycling-shoes.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-adidas-cycling-shoes.jpg\" alt=\"2024 zwift games unlock prizes adidas cycling shoes\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-adidas-cycling-shoes.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-adidas-cycling-shoes-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-adidas-cycling-shoes-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-adidas-cycling-shoes-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-adidas-cycling-shoes-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-adidas-cycling-shoes-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-adidas-cycling-shoes-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Much like modern youth sports, everyone’s a winner just for showing up. Regardless of your rankings, every stage you complete unlocks exclusive digital gear for your avatar. Complete just one stage and you unlock adidas Tempo 3-Stripes BOA Shoes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-oakley-sunglasses.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-oakley-sunglasses.jpg\" alt=\"2024 zwift games unlock prizes oakley sunglasses\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-oakley-sunglasses.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-oakley-sunglasses-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-oakley-sunglasses-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-oakley-sunglasses-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-oakley-sunglasses-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-oakley-sunglasses-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-unlock-oakley-sunglasses-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Complete any two stages and you’ll snag a (virtual) pair of Oakley Sphaera sunglasses. Whether they’re photochromic for those virtual night rides remains to be seen.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/zwift-games-wahoo-kickr-bike-gold-prize.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1166\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/zwift-games-wahoo-kickr-bike-gold-prize.jpg\" alt=\"2024 zwift games unlock prizes wahoo kickr bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/zwift-games-wahoo-kickr-bike-gold-prize.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/zwift-games-wahoo-kickr-bike-gold-prize-297x173.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/zwift-games-wahoo-kickr-bike-gold-prize-800x466.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/zwift-games-wahoo-kickr-bike-gold-prize-120x70.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/zwift-games-wahoo-kickr-bike-gold-prize-768x448.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/zwift-games-wahoo-kickr-bike-gold-prize-1536x895.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But if you do win for real, the top competitors in each discipline will take home a custom gold-and-black Wahoo KICKR Bike!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Elite-level Cycling E-Sports broadcasts</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-concept-z1-virtual-gold-tron-bike.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-concept-z1-virtual-gold-tron-bike.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-concept-z1-virtual-gold-tron-bike.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-concept-z1-virtual-gold-tron-bike-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-concept-z1-virtual-gold-tron-bike-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-concept-z1-virtual-gold-tron-bike-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-concept-z1-virtual-gold-tron-bike-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-concept-z1-virtual-gold-tron-bike-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024-zwift-games-concept-z1-virtual-gold-tron-bike-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>More than 300 elite athletes from 33 countries will be racing (<a href=\"https://zwiftgames.link/startlist\" target=\"_blank\">check the start list here</a>), and all of their races will be broadcast live on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLjaxpWLm1cBf3GklheqJ2-4TvWDWJUKOY\" target=\"_blank\">Zwift’s YouTube channel</a>. Schedule is:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Sprint Championship:</strong> Men’s 3/2 6pm UTC / Women’s 3/3 6pm UTC</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Epic Championship:</strong> Men’s 3/9 6pm UTC / Women’s 3/10 6pm UTC</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Sprint Championship:</strong> Men’s 3/16 6pm UTC / Women’s 3/17 6pm UTC</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The overall winner with the best combined results from all three stages only gets the Wahoo KICKR Bike IRL, they’ll also get a gold Concept Z1 bike to ride in-game for a year. After that, they’ll need to defend their title in next year’s Games.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://news.zwift.com/en-WW/234748-everything-you-need-to-know-about-the-inaugural-zwift-games\" target=\"_blank\">Zwift.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2024-zwift-games/\">Zwift Games Start in March – Here’s How to Compete</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"ab27bd7317bcf1728d963f51eea91bc6d423a340ccb09ff986484f6553904c9a","category":"Cycling"}